1. Moj kolega je postao predsednik *odbora* za obrazovanje. (My colleague became the president of the *committee* for education.)
2. Odluka o tome će biti doneta na sledećem *odboru*. (The decision on that will be made at the next *meeting* of the committee.)
3. *Odbor* za ljudska prava je organizovao konferenciju o diskriminaciji. (The *committee* for human rights organized a conference on discrimination.)
4. Naša firma je donirala novac *odboru* za zaštitu životne sredine. (Our company donated money to the *committee* for environmental protection.)
5. *Odbor* za izbor studenata sastavljen je od profesora sa fakulteta. (The *committee* for selecting students is composed of professors from the faculty.)
6. Molim te, pročitaj izveštaj *odobra* pre nego što dođeš na sastanak. (Please read the report of the *committee* before you come to the meeting.)
7. Predložio sam svoje ideje na sastanku *odobra* i dobio sam pozitivan odgovor. (I proposed my ideas at the *committee* meeting and received a positive response.)
8. *Odbor* za bezbednost je odobrio plan za zaštitu objekta od požara. (The *committee* for safety approved the plan for protecting the building from fire.)